metadata.name: Tezumie #692
metadata.description:
Tezumie are interdimensional beings who seemingly spawn out of thin air. Tezumie are obsessed with Eating, fighting, and Collecting junk they find throughout the universe. Once a Token is minted, you will spawn your very own Tezumie! 

Beware, there is more to them than they let on. They are not Restricted to the blockchain, and you may notice strange things appearing and disappearing around you. You have been warned.

Project Created thanks to the PureSpider FXHASH PFP Token Generator.

metadata.name: Crude Acceptance #73
metadata.description:
It was there when we arrived
    No owners, no gatekeepers
    The opportunity to explore
    The chance to transform
    What we are
    What we see
    And a trace will came with us
    And that way it will multiply
    As long as we allow
    To leave here a part of us
    It will be there when we leave
    No owners, no gatekeepers
    But itself



  Controls
  Format:
  'f' - switch square/full screen format

  View:

  'Arrow Up/Down' - Decrease/Increase distance to origin
  'Mouse Drag' - View Rotation


  Export:
  'x' - show/hide export menu
  'm' - quick canvas save


Created with p5.js (Javascript + GLSL) by Victor Doval @vicdoval (2022)
Designed to be seen in Google Chrome 102.0.5005.63

metadata.name: 2D Mansion #740
metadata.description:
A mansion generator to crash real estate prices.

Press 'n' or click on the sun to cycle day/night, 's' toggle the canvas resizing and allows to zoom or take a picture at full resolution.

Guest has 7 different values (Two can only happen at a certain moon phase) and there are 4 different materials.
